articles.title: Cyclone Freddy kills 190 in Malawi as rain complicates rescue efforts - Reuters
articles.description: Cyclone Freddy, one of the most powerful storms ever recorded in the southern hemisphere, has killed 190 people in Malawi after ripping through southern Africa for the second time in a month, Malawi's government said on Tuesday.
